MDG WEBSITE — PHOTO ASSETS
==========================

Drop your photos into the subfolders following the naming and size guidelines
in each folder's instructions. Once all photos are in place, let Claude know
and they will be wired into the website automatically.

FOLDER OVERVIEW
---------------
people/founders/    Headshots of the 4 co-founders
people/team/        Headshots of the 7 executive team members
projects/           Card thumbnails + hero banners for each project (4 projects)
programs/           Card thumbnails + hero banners for each program (4 programs)
philosophy/         3 thematic images for the Tri Hita Karana section
news/               Cover images for news/blog articles

GENERAL RULES
-------------
- Format:     JPG preferred (JPEG). PNG is also fine.
- Colour:     Natural, warm tones work best with the site's terracotta palette.
              Avoid heavily filtered or cold-toned images.
- File names: Exactly as specified in each folder. Lowercase, hyphens, no spaces.
- No spaces or special characters in filenames.
